<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Navigation_Page_Mvc requires the front controller's router to have a getRoute() method that is missing in Zend_Controller_Router_Interface</p>

<p>This can break an application using custom routers (such as CLI or cross application ones)</p>

